Michael Sundin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Sundin 0 Michael Sundin (1 March 1961 – 23 July 1989) was an English television presenter, actor, dancer and trampolinist. He was a presenter of the BBC children's programme Blue Peter presenter for 77 episodes between 1984 and 1985.
